                <div class="stack-col">
                    <h4>Daily</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Creatine, 5g</li>
                        <li>Vitamin D + K2</li>
                        <li>Magnesium, evenings</li>
                        <li>Electrolytes, mornings</li>
                        <li>Black coffee</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p class="stack-note">Boring on purpose. Nothing exotic.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="stack-col">
                    <h4>Gear</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Barbell + plates</li>
                        <li>A pair of shoes worth walking in</li>
                        <li>Cast iron + sharp knife</li>
                        <li>Blackout curtains</li>
